Full Description: Spamedik (derived from "Spa Medika") is a deal-of-the-day website that features discounted gift certificates usable at local or national specialized Beauty & Aesthetic Skincare or Clinics. Spamedik was launched in January 2014, and the first market for Spamedik was Jakarta, followed soon to another Cities in Indonesia The idea for Spamedik was created by Founder CEO and Co Founder Indonesian native dr. Reza Yuridian, SpKK & Michael Raharjo. Selected clinics - skincare, beauty shops. All selected from high quality, well-known and trusted Skincare brands and just transformed to Online as additional super service for the customer. We are the bridge between well-known beauty & aesthetic clinics and online customer. A business strategy We sell and deliver goods and discount voucher from well-known Skincare & Beauty Clinics through our online website (www.spamedik.com), as well as through other available channels (Call-Center, BBM, Skype, Chat, Social Media, etc). On the first stage we are focusing for placing Skincare discounts, skin treatment products, online consultation and Online Magazine. We are focusing on this segment on the first stage because the niche is still empty and we feel really uncovered demand for these categories in online retail, if done very well. We are creating a Great service from the beginning, so customer able to choose the best treatment price according to their needs. On the second stage (dates undefined yet, but at least after 6 months from launch) we will try to add more categories to the site, Online Consultation and other possible stuff that fits to our business…
